{"tid":1672683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"作左首歌比時事台手足 咁都無人講？","createTime":"2019-10-24T09:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T10:09:10.000Z","uid":142433,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f74d11424edb56b9f37e47161c75e49c3a17b980","tid":1672683,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:00:32.000Z","msg":"五毛鬧我 我就會講：不分化切割<br />\n有同路見無力 有話要講：躝開啦加泰<br />\n<br />\n我不推文 又亂拉post <br />\n專業法師、核彈也在CC台<br />\n戰場外 我們在上lin登 攞着尾彩 <br />\n目的想搞出大台<br />\n<br />\n見無人 就吹風 我們被嘴炮就只有敵人<br />\n我遇見即block 你無得反駁 <br />\nsolomon帶領叫你地借開！<br />\n<br />\n你這叫杜蕾斯吧？ 休息 今天我不了<br />\n扔氣油 扔石係鬼做 即刻要切割<br />\n其實怕被忘記 至放大來演吧：<br />\n1.「裝修都不夠優雅」<br />\n2.「美帝唔撐我地」<br />\n3.「核彈！」<br />\n4.「推到爆炸！」<br />\n5.「加狗有自由」<br />\n6.「就快輸」<br />\n7.「Oh say can you see~」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60eeda44fbbdaf613996cd2174883b14d33271c9","tid":1672683,"uid":110699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:01:30.000Z","msg":"完全唔想推"},{"pid":"0bd111d8a3293c001e3da92b7f6fa426a3cf2048","tid":1672683,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:04:01.000Z","msg":"唉 場運動完左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca4dd04bc96553e352040ee08fb4b735b629c7b","tid":1672683,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:06:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"137d7df8b19ec2ad1ea9774f0f7c23c008ea5af2","tid":1672683,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:06:53.000Z","msg":"今場運動係咪無人再出黎架啦"},{"pid":"60674c8b81f6d435356ff7c89ba58be1ac933847","tid":1672683,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:08:00.000Z","msg":"(核彈)推到爆炸！"},{"pid":"16632f8674fb6cfa22aa7354b55cd379ad2baa1d","tid":